These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, collecting, traveling, sudoku
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, classical, disco, country
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, october, november, september
4 different pets are kept: goat, chinchilla, goldfish, snake
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, iris, bellflower, marigold
 1. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the person who growsmarigold##3
 2. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere to the left of the fan of country##5
 3. the fan of classical is on the far left##1
 4. the fan of house is the owner of the chinchilla##1
 5. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the fan of house##1
 6. the owner of the chinchilla is not to the left of the person who growsiris##8
 7. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 8. the owner of the goldfish is not to the left of the person who growspoppy##8
 9. the person who growsmarigold is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
10. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##5
11. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an even position##4
12. the person who growsbellflower is on the left or right of the person who growspoppy##3
13. the person who's birthday is in september is not to the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##8
14. the person who growsbellflower is somewhere to the left of the person who growsmarigold##5
15. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goldfish##5
16. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the owner of the snake##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |      3       |      4      |
| Hobby    | sudoku | collecting     | traveling     | hiking |
| Music-Genre        | classical  | house | disco      | country      |
| Birthday         | september  | october    | november | july       |
| Pet       | goat | chinchilla   | goldfish      | snake  |
| Flower   | iris      | poppy  | bellflower   | marigold      |

